Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1402,196)}裤头村站
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.58,0:01:05.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沉船镇  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:05.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jetsam City, here I come
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.54,0:01:08.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定会是史上最棒周末
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:08.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be the best weekend ever
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.84,0:01:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.59,0:01:14.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:14.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.22,0:01:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你该不会也要去沉船镇漫展吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:15.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Jetsam City comic convention too
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.72,0:01:20.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:20.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would I waste my time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.26,0:01:22.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去逛什么白痴漫展
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:22.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on an idiotic comic book convention?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.81,0:01:25.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有着深深的文化造诣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:25.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a man of sophistication
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.56,0:01:28.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去竖笛大会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:28.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the clarinet convention
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.19,0:01:30.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:30.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.11,0:01:32.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫浪费时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:32.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talk about a waste of time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少不懂装懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shows what you know
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.74,0:01:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单是听个竖笛口水阀历史讲座
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lecture on the history of spit valves
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都能值回票价了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is worth the price of admission alone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我之前说这才叫浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I said talk about a waste of time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不单单是说着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean literally
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.62,0:01:49.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往沉船镇的旅客请上车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:49.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All aboard for the train to Jetsam City
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just stay away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dit to the O
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.43,0:02:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dibs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续走吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep walking, Bucko
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.57,0:02:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你连占了两个座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're taking up two seats
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一边屁股一个座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One for each cheek
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我挪过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just move over
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,车上位置就剩这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the last seat on the train
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别找我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't talk to me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早都吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's finished
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.47,0:02:49.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那看来还要再来点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:49.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then it appears I need another snack
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.85,0:02:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪火锅车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fondue cart
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪火锅车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fondue cart
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要奶酪火锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fondue, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.03,0:03:01.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请给我来一大碗热到冒泡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:01.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One bubbling bowl of melted cheese, please
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你运气正好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're in luck, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.82,0:03:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正好现做了热气腾腾的一大盘出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just made a fresh, piping hot batch
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要多大的火锅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What size would you like?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特地自带了个锅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought my own fondue pot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,装满吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fill it to the rim
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小小小  小心点倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be-be-be careful with that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一站  沉船镇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next stop, Jetsam City
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吃不吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you going to eat that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off of me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(818,892)}艺术
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay on your side
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.20,0:03:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可真是一对好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, aren't you two the best of friends
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are not
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能帮忙照看我宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you watch my baby
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得先去一趟卫生间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I run to the restroom?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要方便很久才能出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to powder my nose like a racehorse
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.34,0:04:06.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐火车就是这个下场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:06.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is what I get for traveling coach
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.97,0:04:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪火锅吃得我都流奶酪汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That fondue gave me the cheese sweats
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Refreshing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都快害宝宝着凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're making the baby cold
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上哪找来这么可爱的宝宝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did you get such an adorable baby?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他肯定是要开窗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who clearly wants the window open
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝要关窗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The baby wants it closed
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.12,0:04:35.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝要开窗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:35.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The baby wants it open
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关窗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Closed
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.00,0:04:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开窗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关窗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Closed
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.25,0:04:37.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开窗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:37.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The baby
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm back
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's my baby?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really want to know?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望她能找到宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope she finds her baby
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.10,0:04:54.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,查票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:54.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tickets
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,查票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tickets
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,查票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tickets?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没票是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No tickets, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I loathe you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等妈妈找到那俩家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When Mommy finds those two
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会禁足他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,she's gonna ground them
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,化他们为灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Into dust
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能走过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm walking
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不带点吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without snacks?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我快饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该不会喜欢我饿肚子的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't like me when I'm hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在就不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't like you now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就快死在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to die out here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不至于
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe not
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老头简金斯有块地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old Man Jenkins has a farm
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,农场里有交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And on that farm, he has a ride?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咿呀咿呀哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,E-I-E-I-O
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这有拖拉机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With a tractor here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那有小马驹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And some horsies there
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.87,0:05:56.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有条船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here a boat
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.87,0:05:57.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There a bike
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有靴子能徒步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everywhere are boots to hike
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老头简金斯有飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old Man Jenkins has a plane
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咿呀咿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,E-I-E-I-
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.46,0:06:05.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:05.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢你载我们一程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the ride
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也谢谢你送的鸡蛋沙拉三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the egg salad sandwiches
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.85,0:06:17.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们运气正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:17.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You folks are lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正要去沉船镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just heading into the city
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.90,0:06:21.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,领取新出的农夫年鉴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:21.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to pick up the new Farmer's Almanac
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To celebrate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.32,0:06:25.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种三明治我得再吃一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:25.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I will have another one of those sandwiches
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚吃过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just ate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快够到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can almost reach
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别乱摇飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop shaking the plane
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我马上迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'll pull this thing right over
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Much better
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.34,0:06:45.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:45.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what do we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.30,0:06:50.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以把机尾当黄包车  我来坐你来拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:50.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You could pull me using the plane tail as a rickshaw
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.68,0:06:51.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我拉你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:51.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me pull you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都要怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your fault
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你才得拉我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should pull me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,翻硬币决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll flip a coin
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,翻就翻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're on
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我够不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't reach
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能捞出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you fish it out?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算你赢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You win
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:15.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(478,584)}欢迎光临\N沉船镇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:18.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1016,196)}拖船大酒店
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别把油漆刮花了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't scratch the paint
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,零钱不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep the change
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.55,0:07:37.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥预定的客房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:37.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reservation for Squidward Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王也预定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生和海霸王先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tentacles and Mr. Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.98,0:07:46.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个预定了我们最好的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:46.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two have reserved our finest rooms
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以拿钥匙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we just get our keys?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们昨天就应该来登记入住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to check in yesterday
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果却爽约了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.87,0:07:57.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以房间送别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:57.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we gave your rooms away
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.17,0:08:07.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看还能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:07.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see what we can do
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过比你们之前预约的房间烂一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Though it's not as nice as
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your previous accommodations
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就住一晚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just for one night
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能烂到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How bad can it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.43,0:08:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不算太烂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, this isn't so bad
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以给你洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The shower's all yours
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm tired
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱咋咋地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep to your side
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吃得床上到处是碎屑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're getting crumbs in the bed
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去卫生间睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep in the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.04,0:08:48.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:48.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他果然把卫生间全搞乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course he destroyed the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.01,0:08:56.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过  这还挺高档
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:56.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But hey, this is fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毛地毯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shag carpeting
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是地毯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not carpet
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.85,0:09:07.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的体毛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:07.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this your body hair?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The horror
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还挺高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you look chipper
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨晚睡得舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.17,0:09:27.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:27.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.83,0:09:31.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你马上就要参加垃圾漫展去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:31.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But soon you'll be at your lame comic convention
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以离我远远的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,far away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.38,0:09:36.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这倒能让我开心几下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:36.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is something to smile about
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Agreed
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.05,0:09:41.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你的竖笛大会更是垃圾多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:41.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But your Clarinet Con is, by far, the lamer of the two
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漫画书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Comic books
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我们竖笛家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least we clarinetists
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不会披着白痴披风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't wear stupid capes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,500)}欢迎各路阿宅书呆
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老头简金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old Man Jenkins?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.91,0:10:11.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:11.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gadzooks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.44,0:10:32.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,降落只要能成功逃生  就还算可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:32.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any landing you can walk away from is a good landing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无辜的漫画书  全没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All those innocent comic books, lost
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.49,0:10:46.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打脸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:46.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In your face
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还能去参加竖笛大会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still get to go to my clarinet convention
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么都看不着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you get nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You lose
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.85,0:11:03.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最烂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:03.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Worst
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.68,0:11:04.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:04.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trip
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非这莫属
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did everybody go?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,火车站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The train station
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(686,454)}开往  裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.65,0:11:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无票不得乘车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No tickets, no ride
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们还欠我半架飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You boys owe me half a plane
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slow down
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你快伤到我胳膊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're hurting my arms
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们就在那  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There they are, Junior
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,追过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.55,0:11:44.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨你  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:44.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I loathe you, chum
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.77,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}章鱼狂想盒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(702,372)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:57.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(632,450)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(770,648)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(726,542)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(558,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.36,0:12:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清理阁楼的事情都拖了好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have put off cleaning my attic for way too long
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗小时候的壳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary's baby shell
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小孩子长得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They grow up so fast
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的想象力盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My imagination box
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道还能不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it still works
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  现在来启动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, it's time for
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.74,0:12:50.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:50.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's weird
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.79,0:12:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能借杯沙子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow a cup of sand?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我全用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm all out
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.30,0:13:00.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:00.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过启动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it won't start
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看看我能不能让它启动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see if I can get it going
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们需要专业人士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need a professional
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:24.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1102,796)}想象力\N盒子修复站
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.44,0:13:22.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象力盒子修复站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:22.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imagination Box Repair
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the place
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双重波纹3600
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A double corrugated 3600
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.63,0:13:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经有25年没见过这款了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen one of these in 25 years
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What seems to be the problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灵感马达不转了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the inspiration motor won't turn over
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破玩意坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dern thing's on the fritz
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't work
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我看看盖子底下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look under the flap
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题就在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there's your problem
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的盒子有个异想天开垫片烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your box has blown a whimsy gasket
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种东西已经停产了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't make those anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.25,0:14:23.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你们买坐垫堡垒有优惠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:23.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I could give you a great deal on a cushion fort
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(458,182)}出售
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只爱纸盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a cardboard man
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.35,0:14:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这破盒子现在纯垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This dumb ol' box is just junk now
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别踩我沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off my sand
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.86,0:14:49.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在我的想象力盒子里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:49.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Inside my imagination box
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.91,0:14:54.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定是撞到哪里  阴差阳错修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:54.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must have jostled something and fixed it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥一定是迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward must be lost
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迷失在自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lost in his own
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.29,0:15:03.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:03.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在里面啥都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing in here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要手电筒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a flashlight
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象一个手电筒就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just imagine a flashlight
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对就有鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, right
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.72,0:15:16.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象手电筒  手电筒就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:16.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just imagine it and it'll appear
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.89,0:15:18.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:18.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It worked
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走哪里才可以出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, where's the way out of here?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.95,0:15:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个鬼地方怎么出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do I get out of this crazy place?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很简单  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's easy, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你想要去的地方浮现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just visualize where you'd rather be
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我更想离你们远远的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd rather be far away from you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远到奢华海滩度假村去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like at a fancy beach resort
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.64,0:16:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在躺椅上放松
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:16:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And relaxing on a lounge chair
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小啜热带饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sipping a tropical drink
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这想象力也还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe this imagination thing isn't so bad after all
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing now?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们非得问的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you must know
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在在伞底下放松
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm relaxing under an umbrella
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.45,0:16:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周围都是美丽的热带植物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,surrounded by beautiful tropical plants
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来你好像在丛林里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're in a jungle
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not a--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丛林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,jungle?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丛林里不都是危险的动物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't jungles full of dangerous animals?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.22,0:16:34.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:34.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如说可怕的海蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like scary sea snakes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你快救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gotta help me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心海黑豹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And look out for sea panthers
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面什么情况了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's it going in there, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们让情况变得更糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're making everything worse
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能别说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you two clam up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1026,920)}蛤   蜊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忘了提到吃衣服的蛤蜊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot to mention the clothes-eating clams
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨型蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Giant clam
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.26,0:17:18.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:18.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let go
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.68,0:17:21.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:21.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my shirt
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fantastic
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我在丛林里迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm lost in the jungle
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,身上一丝不挂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with no clothes on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's no problem
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.44,0:17:32.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了  你啥都能想象出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:32.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, you can imagine anything
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imagine, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丛林观兽探险还算有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A jungle safari could be fun
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.62,0:17:52.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管想象什么  都不要想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:52.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And whatever you do, don't imagine
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一大群狂奔的海大象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a stampede of sea elephants
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么逃离一大群狂奔的海大象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how to escape from a stampede of sea elephants
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有热气球就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only you had a hot air balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都很想坐热气球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to ride in a balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.97,0:18:39.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有龙卷风就不想了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unless there's a tornado
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,龙卷风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tornado?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道什么东西比龙卷风更棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what's better than a tornado?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡龙卷风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A bubble tornado
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You okay, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.51,0:19:17.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:17.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说丛林里有恐龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, are there dinosaurs in the jungle?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真高兴能看到章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy Squidward's having
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,探险玩得可嗨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,such an exciting adventure
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么逃离这座丛林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do I get out of this jungle?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.74,0:19:48.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试试想象你最爱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:48.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try imagining your favorite place
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.91,0:19:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最爱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Favorite place?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.62,0:19:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爵士俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A jazz club
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有文化的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A place with culture
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.15,0:20:18.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连咖啡都有爵士味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:18.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even the coffee smells like jazz
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沉浸在节奏里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Digging that groove
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We dig it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这咖啡味道像石头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This coffee tastes like rocks
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1156,920)}摇 滚
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋克摇滚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Punk rock?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都发疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's gone crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.89,0:20:52.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来你的想象力有点过于活跃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:52.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like your imagination is overheating
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.39,0:20:54.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脑袋放空一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:54.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try to clear your mind
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脑袋放空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clear my mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.65,0:20:57.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脑袋放空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:57.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clear my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在在哪  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you now, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在一片空白里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in an empty white void
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过起码很宁静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But at least it's peaceful
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来好像是涂鸦次元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds like the Doodle dimension
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.08,0:21:12.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心铅笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:12.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch out for DoodleBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.33,0:21:13.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他长什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:13.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's he look like?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.71,0:21:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他长得有点像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He looks kind of like this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would somebody please--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,告诉我要怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me how--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逃出这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To get out of this--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白痴盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupid box
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是想出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want out?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.44,0:21:42.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,画个出口大门就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:42.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just draw an exit door
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.78,0:21:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没有笔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have a pen
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.70,0:21:46.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:46.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're an octopus
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.86,0:21:48.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全身都是墨水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:48.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're full of ink
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm home
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.64,0:22:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝跟派大星跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did SpongeBob and Patrick run off to?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.60,0:22:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要前往想象力消亡的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the place where imagination goes to die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:21.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1028,640)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.52,0:22:25.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我枯燥没意义的最低工资工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:25.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My dreary, pointless minimum wage job
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.36,0:22:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是那个无聊的蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The good old boring Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.62,0:22:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm actually happy to be back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.83,0:22:38.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能为你点餐吗  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:38.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I take your order, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该提醒下他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Should we tell him?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.46,0:22:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用  一听就知道他很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah, he sounds so happy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.75,0:22:45.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡套餐马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:45.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby combo coming up
